{"tid":1038732,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"（真心求救）入到 UST之後覺得自己好L毒","createTime":"2019-02-27T01:43:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-27T07:38:20.000Z","uid":239350,"like":20,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"b0e20d6756c26254e5352f7e6b7e4ca59d06836c","tid":1038732,"uid":239350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T01:43:13.000Z","msg":"入到U之後入左個 soc, 去左 O camp。但後來發覺自己組同其他d人已經互相認識，我仲係連自己組d人都唔係識曬。就算我知道要識多d人，都好似冇咩機會。有d人仲好似咩 soc都識人（又 hall又其他soc)。中學果時座係班房就慢慢識到人，入到 U之後完全唔同。有冇人可以解答下？"},{"pid":"f0aaac7cce0d65d49a59c9dc31d3138992ccfa03","tid":1038732,"uid":169521,"like":5,"dislike":4,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T01:49:41.000Z","msg":"首先，識得多人唔係重點。<br />\n然後，中學班人日日一齊上堂，食飯，放學，補習，當然慢慢就會熟。<br />\n而你上到大學要揾到一班人經常一齊做野一齊上堂點都難過中學。<br />\n所以你就會有呢種感覺<br />\n(我都係UST人)"},{"pid":"d63f757aaadd14aa96dd39f0870a19d68a2bd85d","tid":1038732,"uid":110858,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T01:57:05.000Z","msg":"入danso啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a7e7f6b674d0099d7f5ca5cbe6df5d645876d11","tid":1038732,"uid":113626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T03:06:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ust好多mk, 班mk自然好易同人熟"},{"pid":"4f1c65f02a3c76e8a36001f909b7e703a72ff086","tid":1038732,"uid":147754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1a7e7f6b674d0099d7f5ca5cbe6df5d645876d11","tid":1038732,"uid":113626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T03:06:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ust好多mk, 班mk自然好易同人熟"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T05:20:17.000Z","msg":"ust真係mk大學黎 我屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c6eec5455f9ed284b7e5324dff6dffaf8b5ffea","tid":1038732,"uid":222038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-27T05:28:58.000Z","msg":"吊那星你淨係識上登網交都無你份啦<br />\n拿拿聲丟爆部手機同